== YAML / Clojure Gotchas

YAMLScript must be valid YAML. No exceptions.

* Spot the problem:
$ ys -e 'say: "number:" 42'

+* Dot escaping
$ ys -e 'say: ."number:" 42'

* Flow Collections
$ ys -le '=>: [1 2 3]'
$ ys -le '=>: .[1 2 3]'
$ ys -le '=>:: [1 2 3]'
$ ys -le '=>:: [1, 2, 3]'

* Duplicate Keys
$ vim dup-keys-data.ys dup-keys-code.ys -O
$ ys -l dup-keys-data.ys
$ ys dup-keys-code.ys


