== YeS Expressions

* Lisp has S-expressions
* YAMLScript has YeS-expressions!!!

   YAMLScript                           Clojure
   -----------                          -------
   a(b c)                               (a b c)
   a()                                  (a)

   operators: + - * / % %% || && == != < > <= >= =~ .. .

   (a + b)                              (_+ a b)
   a / b / c                            (/ a b c)
   a + b * c                            ERROR

   . is the smart-threading operator:
   a.b.3.c()                            (__ a 'b 3 '(c d e))


