== v0 Versioning

* YAMLScript is future proof

* When v0 is stable, it will never break compatibility
* v1 can make any changes it wants without breaking v0

* !yamlscript/v0
* #!/usr/bin/env ys-0

* ys and ys-0 are symlinks:
$ ls -lh $(which ys)*


